Abdullahi Adamu, senator representing Nasarawa west, has assumed office as the national chairman of the All Progressives Congress (APC). Mai Mala Buni, governor of Yobe and immediate past chairman of the APC national caretaker committee, handed over to Adamu on Wednesday. The handing over ceremony took place at the APC national headquarters in Abuja. Adamu was elected as the ruling partyâ€™s chairman at the national convention which took place on Saturday. Below are photos from the handing over ceremony. <img class="alignnone wp-image-681356" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="399" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2.jpeg 2048w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-300x218.jpeg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-1024x743.jpeg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-768x557.jpeg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-1536x1115.jpeg 1536w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-24x17.jpeg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-36x26.jpeg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman2-48x35.jpeg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-681355" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman4.jpeg" alt="" width="550" height="367" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Abdullahi-takes-charge-as-APC-chairman4.jpeg 2048w, htt